# Source Manager — Layer Definitions

# L0: Foundation / Domain — no internal imports
0 config
0 models
0 events
0 aiverify
0 testcrawl

# L1: Persistence / Infrastructure
1 database
1 services/osrm

# L2: Data Access + Enrichment
2 repository
2 projection
2 metadata
2 importer

# L3: Business Logic
3 services
3 seeder

# L4: HTTP
4 handlers
4 api

# Exempt: bootstrap assembles everything
exempt bootstrap
exempt testhelpers
